data.description: Welcome to ''Five Oaks Ranch'' a 10-acre property located in west Fort Pierce, Florida. With over 6,500 square feet under air, this concrete block pool home has unlimited potential. The kitchen is generously oversized making a Chef kitchen dream, formal dining room, open living area with twenty-foot soaring ceilings. The upstairs living area which could be built out or used as a multipurpose room currently host a large second master. The roof is a tile-look metal, rated impact windows and sliding doors. The outdoor patio is built to entertain with an outdoor bathroom, tongue and grove ceilings, inground pool/spa with endless views of the rolling hills. The outbuilding is currently used as a workshop with an open loft on the 2nd floor (would be a great guest house or shop for a contractor
